Aim: The aim is to not die and eliminate as many enenmies as possible.

Objective: The Objective is to be the only team left with as many members as possible having eliminated all enemies in the process.

Maps: Most games are based around the idea of a One-Life-TDM, though a few maps use 3-Lives such as Blitzkrieg. Games are often short, yet there is a time limit that often times is 10 minutes.

Other Information: You cannot join mid-game.

